#### Awards

Among its accolades, *Bandersnatch* secured two [Primetime Emmy Awards](/Primetime_Emmy_Awards) and a [Broadcasting Press Guild](/Broadcasting_Press_Guild) TV and Radio Award in the Innovation category. Charlie Brooker received the Best Game Writing award at the 2018 [Nebula Awards](/Nebula_Awards) in 2019, recognizing his narrative contributions.

